    /**
     * @description Controls access to temporarily held orders for a company.
     * @path /companies/{companyId}/heldOrders/{orderId}
     * @allow (get, list, create, update, delete) - Only authenticated users can access or modify held orders within a company.
     * @principle Company-scoped data access for authenticated users.
